## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/sizeoffsettype">SizeOffsetType</a> - A base template class for the object size visitors.

Used here as a self-documenting way to handle the values rather than using a <code>std::pair</code>.

Definition at line 192 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/analysis/memorybuiltins-h">MemoryBuiltins.h</a>.
